item.title: Adding Teleports
item.dc:creator: @1_pk_ur_s0ul 1 pk ur s0ul
item.description:
@1_pk_ur_s0ul wrote:

You can change the name of the teleports in TextHandler.Java and you can change the coordinates to which each teleport goes is Clickmost.java

Here is an example:

To locate my Varrock teleport or Home teleport I would go into clickingmost.java and search for this

case 10229:

You will see something like this

case 10229: c.toX = ####; c.toY = ####; break;

simply change the numbers to the coordinates you want your home teleport to be at.

any other questions pm me.
